text: Fimir make great use of [[img:icon_slaves]][[/img]]Slaves for manual labor and in sacrificial rites performed for the Dark Gods.
Sacrificing [[img:icon_slaves]][[/img]]Slaves to the Blood God unlocks additional Gifts of Chaos.
Sacrificing [[img:icon_slaves]][[/img]]Slaves to the Plague Lord unlocks additional Gifts of Chaos.
Sacrificing [[img:icon_slaves]][[/img]]Slaves to the Dark Prince unlocks additional Gifts of Chaos.
Sacrificing [[img:icon_slaves]][[/img]]Slaves to the Lord of Change unlocks additional Gifts of Chaos.
Sacrificing [[img:icon_slaves]][[/img]]Slaves to the Fimir Pantheon unlocks additional Gifts of Chaos.
